How to get app package name andapp activity id which app does not have apk file:

how to automate this kind of app: here are step below:

1. first open that app means in home screen will be that app:
2.connect device
2.open terminal
3. type adb shell //to  connect shell
4. / $ dumsys window windows | grep -E 'mCurrentFocus|mFocusedApp'
5. hit enter

in result there will mCurrentFocus = one big line from there value will be two part which will be look like package(like com.gjgh.vhv)


download indeed apk file from google


